<% @page_title = 'Sort order' -%>

<h1>Sort order</h1>

<p>The <b>Person's name</b> data type with the <i>Western</i> name style sorts as:</p>

<p class="z__management_important_value"><%= @person_name_sort_readable %></p>
<% if @person_name_sort == 'last_first' %>
<p>Displayed as: First Last</p>
<% end %>
<%= sys_mng_edit_button("/do/setup/application/edit_sort_order") %>

<p><span class="z__management_look_at_help">Sort order does not affect how names are displayed in objects and search results.</span></p>

<p>The sort order of <i>Eastern</i> and <i>Western List</i> name styles is always <b>Last First</b>.</p>

<% if params.has_key?('changed'.freeze) %>
  <p><b>Sort order update has started.</b><br>Changes to sort order may take a few minutes to apply.</p>
<% end %>
